      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASH ROSE (1) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 17.22. Well suited by the inside box and has the ability and in winning form. Can continue the winning form. REGGAE MELODY (2) placed two back in a Grade 4/5 at this track then not far away from a tricky draw last time when fourth (17.36) at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. JOLLY OLLIE (3) hit the frame after colliding with another runner last time in a Grade 5 at this track, finishing a 3.5 lengths third (17.45). Bold showing expected again. FROMELLES POPPY (7) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this circuit.",
